cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper focuses on adversarial attacks on visual trackers, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) and Siamese networks also suggests that the paper may fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The analysis of vulnerabilities and formulation of the adversarial generation problem also suggests that the paper may fall under cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the experiments conducted involve the use of video and image data, which suggests that the paper may also fall under multimedia (cs.MM).
